## Provider в†” Manager Method Mapping

The following manager classes have been DELETED. Their methods exist in providers:

| Old Manager Method | Provider Replacement |
|---|---|
| `UserManager().name` | `ref.watch(userProvider).name` |
| `UserManager().email` | `ref.watch(userProvider).email` |
| `UserManager().phone` | `ref.watch(userProvider).phone` |
| `UserManager().role` | `ref.watch(userProvider).role` |
| `UserManager().userId` | `ref.watch(userProvider).userId` |
| `UserManager().staffType` | REMOVED вЂ” only 3 roles now |
| `UserManager().profileImage` | `ref.watch(userProvider).profileImage` |
| `UserManager().updateProfile(...)` | `ref.read(userProvider.notifier).updateProfile(...)` |
| `UserManager().logout()` | `ref.read(userProvider.notifier).logout()` |
| `CartManager().addItem(...)` | `ref.read(cartProvider.notifier).addToCart(...)` |
| `CartManager().removeItem(...)` | `ref.read(cartProvider.notifier).removeFromCart(...)` |
| `CartManager().updateQuantity(...)` | `ref.read(cartProvider.notifier).updateQuantity(...)` |
| `CartManager().clearCart()` | `ref.read(cartProvider.notifier).clearCart()` |
| `CartManager().itemCount` | `ref.watch(cartProvider).itemCount` |
| `CartManager().isInCart(...)` | `ref.read(cartProvider.notifier).isInCart(...)` |
| `WishlistManager().addToWishlist(...)` | `ref.read(wishlistProvider.notifier).addToWishlist(...)` |
| `WishlistManager().removeFromWishlist(...)` | `ref.read(wishlistProvider.notifier).removeFromWishlist(...)` |
| `WishlistManager().itemCount` | `ref.watch(wishlistProvider).itemCount` |
| `WishlistManager().isInWishlist(...)` | `ref.read(wishlistProvider.notifier).isInWishlist(...)` |
| `WishlistManager().clearWishlist()` | `ref.read(wishlistProvider.notifier).clearWishlist()` |
| `OrderManager().orderCount` | `ref.watch(orderProvider).orderCount` |
| `OrderManager().addOrder(...)` | `ref.read(orderProvider.notifier).addOrder(...)` |
| `NotificationManager().markAsRead(...)` | `ref.read(notificationProvider.notifier).markAsRead(...)` |

